statements.sql: select `team_channels`.`channel_view_name`, `team_channels`.`team_channel_id`, `team_channels`.`id` from `team_channels` left join `team_channel_users` on `team_channel_users`.`team_channel_name_id` = `team_channels`.`id` where `team_channel_users`.`user_id` = '8'
select `users`.`first_name`, `users`.`id` from `users` left join `team_channel_users` on `team_channel_users`.`user_id` = `users`.`id` where `team_channel_users`.`team_channel_name_id` = '4'
